# removed from history 2026-07-11 (dead prototype: stale .next/ cache +
# __MACOSX junk baked into the zip, no secrets found) — kept on disk
# untracked in case it's still wanted for reference, must never be re-added.
packages/net-content-provider/front_nextjs/Archive.zip

